: Giorgio Barroccu, Web Designer Freelance&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/wordpress-meetup-genova/events/298858363\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Napoli</h2><p>gio 22 feb, ore 18:00, &#8221; &#8211; Ottieni il massimo dalle Lead di WordPress&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/wordpress-napoli-meetup/events/298949689\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Terni</h2><p>gio 22 feb, ore 19:00, &#8220;Full Site Editing, ora WordPress ragiona così&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/wordpress-meetup-terni/events/298798206\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Roma</h2><p>mer 28 feb, ore 18:00, &#8220;WordPress e ChatGPT: come automatizzare i processi di creazione contenuti&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/romawordpress/events/299036025\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Treviso</h2><p>gio 29 feb, ore 19:30, &#8220;Le novità di WordPress, febbraio 2024&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/treviso-wordpress-meetup/events/298839307\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p><div style=\"height:var(--wp--preset--spacing--50)\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div><p class=\"has-text-align-center has-dark-blueberry-color has-blueberry-3-background-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color has-extra-large-font-size\">… articolo in aggiornamento…</p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:75:\"https://it.wordpress.org/news/2024/02/tutti-i-meetup-di-febbraio-2024/f